EZ77UYY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fh_YVVBaWAsq9gpNnX07BGmF7Hno%3D%2F1095x727%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOL765EAMAVCTVLSAZRXEZ77UYY.jpg&h=b652357c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國網友在網路爆料前女友跟金主「滾床單」事件。圖為網友宣稱當事女子。翻攝微博"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T07:50:12.000Z","msg":"似有D年紀, 點值1.5億呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T08:49:27.000Z","msg":"用公司錢投資咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1b80453ccc3575f5f3f5c87dad7fde9fb8f7fc","tid":2253504,"uid":30067,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T11:16:55.000Z","msg":"一定屌<br />\n屌到佢生孖胎"},{"pid":"ca546374f2619e1ea8ca2704d1e2e860adafaeba","tid":2253504,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T11:18:00.000Z","msg":"億幾既床單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a918a73806b0ef9e7860d1f90685407471ca5b1f","tid":2253504,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T11:24:46.000Z","msg":"推 黃之鋒：航空業界無論罷工定訂曬全球豬嘴返香港 一直有力出力 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2252268\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2252268</a>"},{"pid":"c3cb40c1ab998c29032e1e9aea02ba0eeeed9385","tid":2253504,"uid":90442,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T11:28:47.000Z","msg":"好正常，0.1%佣都15萬<br />\n<br />\nD有錢佬預左比佣姐，唔一定要搵你買，可以搵第二個肯上床既買"},{"pid":"a897033993466a726741c63c55c67e7cf8c93208","tid":2253504,"uid":127905,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T11:45:06.000Z","msg":"個金主啲口味咁奇怪"},{"pid":"cf9f7792f6a28815448cf8e98d07cc4c567462da","tid":2253504,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T11:45:25.000Z","msg":"係大陸依d係新聞咩<im